# Demo Builder — Construction Company Website

**Slug:** `construction-company-website`
**Demo:** Cornerstone Construction Co.
**Build status:** COMPLETE
**Build type:** Full build, self-contained static app (no bundler)
**Feature richness:** 10/10

---

## What Was Built

A four-page construction company marketing website at:
`../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/construction-company-website/`

---

## File Manifest

| File | Size | Role |
|---|---|---|
| `index.html` | 16 KB | Home: video hero, stats, services teaser, featured projects, testimonials, CTA, footer |
| `services.html` | 19 KB | Services: 3 service sections with pricing tiers, FAQ accordion, CTA, footer |
| `projects.html` | 16 KB | Projects: filter bar, 9 project cards, lightbox modal, CTA, footer |
| `contact.html` | 16 KB | Contact: info panel, validated form, success state, footer |
| `style.css` | 37 KB | Full design system: tokens, layout, components, page-level, responsive, sr-only utility |
| `main.js` | 7 KB | Nav transparency/scroll, hamburger drawer, scroll fade-in, stats counter, FAQ accordion (aria-expanded fixed) |
| `projects.js` | 11 KB | Filter (aria-pressed fixed), lightbox (arrow nav, keyboard ESC/arrows, focus trap) |
| `contact.js` | 5 KB | Form validation (blur + submit), success state with first name |
| `assets/hero.mp4` | 6.8 MB | Hero video (local, same-origin, downloaded from Pexels) |
| `assets/hero-poster.jpg` | 583 KB | Hero poster fallback (local, from Unsplash) |

Total: 8 source files + 2 binary assets. Within 12-file cap.

---

## Requirements Coverage

| Requirement | Implemented | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Video background homepage | YES | `<video autoplay muted loop playsinline>` with `assets/hero.mp4` (same-origin). JS timeout + error fallback to poster. |
| Services page with pricing | YES | 3 full service sections, each with 3 pricing tiers in a styled card |
| Contact page with form | YES | Full Name, Email, Phone, Service selector, Description, Contact method radio. Blur + submit validation. Inline errors. Animated success state. |
| Projects gallery | YES | 9 projects (3 per category), instant filter tabs, lightbox with arrow nav, ESC close, keyboard nav, focus trap |
| Construction industry theme | YES | Charcoal Black + Safety Amber palette, Oswald + DM Sans + Archivo, inline SVG icons, full-bleed imagery |
| Professional UX/UI | YES | Sticky transparent-to-solid nav, scroll-fade-in sections, hover states, animated stats counters, hamburger mobile menu |
| Testimonials | YES | 2 testimonial cards with amber left-border accent and curly-quote styling |
| Stats counters | YES | easeOutQuad RAF animation on IntersectionObserver trigger |
| Mobile hamburger | YES | Morph animation (3 lines to X), slide-in drawer, ESC + overlay close |
| FAQ accordion | YES | 4 questions on services page, smooth max-height slide, aria-expanded toggled on open/close |
| WCAG / Reduced-motion | YES | prefers-reduced-motion guard in JS and CSS. aria-label, role, aria-current, aria-required throughout. |
| No em/en dashes | YES | Verified clean with grep across all files including workSamples.js |
| workSamples.js entry | YES | id: 8, registered with correct schema |

