## Fixes Applied During This Review Pass

1. **`.sr-only` missing** — `projects.html` uses `class="sr-only"` on a visually-hidden h2. Added standard sr-only utility class to `style.css`.
2. **FAQ `aria-expanded` static** — `main.js` FAQ handler now toggles `aria-expanded` on the button and `aria-hidden` on the answer panel on each click.
3. **Filter `aria-pressed` static** — `projects.js` filter handler now updates `aria-pressed` on all filter buttons on each click.
4. **Em dash in `workSamples.js`** — `client: "Upwork — Construction Company Owner"` replaced with comma separator.

