## Notes for Proposal Writer

- **Demo name:** Cornerstone Construction Co. Website Demo
- **Live URL:** `https://michaelwegter.com/demos/construction-company-website/`
- **Key differentiators to highlight:**
  1. Video hero done correctly: same-origin MP4, autoplay/muted/loop, overlay for legibility, JS error fallback to poster
  2. Pricing transparency on Services page (differentiator in construction market, most firms hide prices)
  3. Filterable project gallery across all 3 service lines with full lightbox detail view
  4. Bespoke industrial design: charcoal + safety amber, Oswald headlines, zero template feel
  5. Mobile-first responsive, WCAG AA baseline, prefers-reduced-motion respected
- **"Medium rare" brief:** Address this directly in the cover letter. Show you understood: executed with confidence and precision, not raw (placeholder-heavy) and not overdone (animation-heavy).
- **Proposal design:** Use Oswald for headlines and DM Sans for body in the one-pager and deck. Palette: `#0D0F12` bg, `#E8991A` amber accent, `#F0EDE8` white. Not michaelwegter.com's look.
